  "name": "RPlog_A_Cunning_Plan",
  "title": "A Cunning Plan",
  "summary": "In the Coral Gardens of Mon Calamari's Coral City, the Corellian musician Paul Nighman plays guitar while the precocious, red-haired boy Kian trades sly banter with General Skeezix Calhoun and the copper-haired Gabrielle. Beneath the lazy afternoon chatter, Kian needles the General about 'real battles' with a wit that hints he is far cleverer than his years, while Paul grows visibly troubled whenever talk turns to the army and basic training. After the others drift off, Paul chases the General down on North Coral Avenue and introduces himself, raising his concern about a young woman named Shenner, whom he believes is rashly considering enlistment partly because of feelings she has developed for him. Skeezix coolly insists the choice is Shenner's alone but agrees to talk to her, and Paul, sensing further pressure would backfire, withdraws, doubting the General's notion of what is 'wise' will match his own.",
